replies.msg:
Sarri on N'Golo Kante: &quot;The problems are only the results because when we won, the position of N'Golo was good. At the moment we are not winning, so it is normal that some players are playing very badly or in the wrong positions. It is normal.&quot; <br />
<br />
&quot;I can understand why you or someone else doesn't agree, but I have explaind why [we play Kante in a more attacking role], really well.&quot;

Sarri on win: &quot;We had Eden for the first time in that position. I think for the first 20-25 minutes we didn't defend well in the opponents half, fortunately we defended well in our own. After the goal the game changed, I think.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;I'm very happy but now we need to play with this level of determination, with the right aggression, in the other matches. Otherwise it's useless to win a match like this&quot;

